title: Muddy Waters - The Lost Tapes (Live,1971)
description:
Muddy Waters
The Lost Tapes (1971)

Recorded live in 1971. (in London?)


Tracks: 
1. Introduction 
2. Honey Bee 
3. Hoochie Coochie Man 
4. Walking Thru The Park 
5. Trouble No More 
6. Just To Be With You 
7. Muddy's Introduction To "19 Years Old" 
8. She's 19 Years Old 
9. Long Distance Call 
10. Mannish Boy 
11. Crawlin' Kingsnake 
12. Got My Mojo Working 
13. Hold It 


Muddy Waters (vocals, slide guitar); 
Sammy Lawhorn, Pee Wee Madison (guitar); 
George "Harmonica" Smith (harmonica); 
Pinetop Perkins (piano); 
Calvin "Fuzz" Jones (bass); 
Willie "Big Eyes" Smith (drums).
